mint.t.sol
├── when the caller is not the owner
│   └── it should revert
└── when the caller is the owner
    ├── given mintPermittedAfter is in the future
    │   └── it should revert
    ├── given mintPermittedAfter is 0 (first mint)
    │   ├── when the amount exceeds the maxSupply
    │   │   └── it should revert
    │   └── when the amount is lte the maxSupply
    │       └── it should mint the tokens to the specified account
    └── given mintPermittedAfter is in the past
        ├── when the amount exceeds the mint cap
        │   └── it should revert
        └── when the amount is within the mint cap
            ├── it should mint the tokens to the specified account
            ├── it should update the mintPermittedAfter
            └── it should emit a TokensMinted event
